      <title>渣打银行首席执行官温特斯会见中国外汇监管机构并成立投资银行部门</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-ceo-winters-meets-china-fx-regulator-launches-investment-banking-unit-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行首席执行官比尔·温特斯(Bill Winters)周一会见了中国外汇监管机构负责人，一个月前，渣打银行暂停了中国客户通过配额渠道对离岸产品的新投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-ceo-winters-meets-china-fx-regulator-launches-investment-banking-unit-2024-03-26/</guid>
