      <title>前中国足协主席在全面打击腐败后被判无期徒刑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/ex-head-china-football-association-sentenced-life-prison-state-media-report-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据官方媒体周二报道，中国国家足球协会前主席陈戌源因受贿被判处无期徒刑，此前这是足球界多年来最大规模的反腐败调查之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/ex-head-china-football-association-sentenced-life-prison-state-media-report-2024-03-26/</guid>
