      <title>美元下跌，日元从东京的言论中获得支撑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-dips-yen-draws-support-tokyos-jawboning-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于获利回吐以及日元小幅走强的压力，美元周二处于不利地位，因为日本政府官员继续大肆宣扬捍卫日元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-dips-yen-draws-support-tokyos-jawboning-2024-03-26/</guid>
